description: A woman is arrested after the death of a 33-year-old man in a garden in Gorey, County Wexford.
title: Gorey: Man dies after suspected stabbing in Wexford
title_page: Gorey: Man dies after suspected stabbing in Wexford - BBC News
maintext: They found the 33-year-old man in the garden with "apparent stab wounds". He was given medical treatment but was later pronounced dead at the scene.
